text: Max Arno Rascher (October 29, 1879 - February 19, 1965) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1965 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
